Summary

Dataset: Malawi

Outcome variable: MDAT language at Midline (l20 - l48)

Comparison variable: Gender (Male, Female)

Items with no variance: none

Items with no variance within levels of comparison variable: none

Bias detection method: IRT

Total number of biased items: 2 out of 26

Type of item bias: non-uniform
